881b395a6afb36df","tid":185296,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Work-life balance有咩錯？<br />\nOt本身係效率低既表現黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係，我公司啲人日日都超準時放工，大把時間做自己野對員工係好事，諗唔明懶死唔走開ot為乜鳩"},{"pid":"33bbcda1cd22b5836a977844b56050b9882ba158","tid":185296,"uid":102442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"又係度培養奴性"},{"pid":"2c9bf385915512fa48b3c98c2194e2f1d01ee5a3","tid":185296,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"晴報專訊呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04cc38fc5a2b2278992148c74b9c9429aa62f6b","tid":185296,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我屌你老母臭化閪逗你果雞碎咁多人工想搵人同你做狗搏命你冇撚野下化？</span>"},{"pid":"f0131a079f888d90d720b0cd6e8da99f787d2804","tid":185296,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"我簽約係賣身唔賣靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0859c7e94b4499634df77d3f7db08ad91acab43","tid":185296,"uid":5900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"成日講咩獅子山精神<br />\n廿幾三十年喇，重講呢啲就知社會無進步過"},{"pid":"1cb465c2c8eae5f8b7780c823ff4c29f34967a5f","tid":185296,"uid":101811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"時代唔同係咁咖啦<br />\n以為既人努力做野好易改變生活<br />\n宜家就算我地辛苦讀完書出嚟咪又係搵得少少錢<br />\n最憎d人成日話年輕一代點點點 成日用d舊思想套落新時代"},{"pid":"4289c6af057008ebaa344f9d09a7617b592097d4","tid":185296,"uid":101811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時代唔同係咁咖啦<br 